This paper discusses the use of SDN and NFV in 5G networks for network slicing, which falls under the category of network infrastructure (cs.NI) and system and control (cs.SY). The paper also covers topics related to cloud computing (cs.DC), information theory (cs.IT), and computer engineering (cs.CE).
